{"tid":1258810,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[屌]香港基本法權力原來係北京賞賜","createTime":"2019-06-26T09:43:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T16:20:21.000Z","uid":4672,"like":3,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5097da06e9c2d1652e84481fdf17fe170dc7ef1c","tid":1258810,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T09:43:58.000Z","msg":"「基本法解釋權屬於中央人民政府」<br />\n「香港行政長官由中央人民政府任命」<br />\n「修改基本法需要立法會+ 全港人大 經2/3同意 並&ldquo;呈請&rdquo;北京（未必同意）」<br />\n<br />\n但民主基礎價值係 人民 <br />\n「由人民賦予權力 政府需得到人民授權而管治 <br />\n並接受人民監督」<br />\n<br />\n各國憲法就係一份份由人民授權政府的法律<br />\n而香港基本法 完全一部假憲法 <br />\n其內在是徹頭徹尾的威權主義 <br />\n並非由人民賦予 而係北京俾你 你先有<br />\n佢話俾幾多你 你就得幾多<br />\n<br />\n事實證明威權和民主不可能並存<br />\n如果此法律非人民所意 為何香港人要守呢種法律？"},{"pid":"5ad9fed887ddcc27dc73f9ec957818a3249eafc1","tid":1258810,"uid":35842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T09:44:56.000Z","msg":"只有一國一制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XQQREDk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXQQREDk.png&h=190dd71d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n2LmYZa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn2LmYZa.png&h=1855d90a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n前立法局主席黃宏發踢爆：<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">議事規則得撤回 押後 postpone or withdraw</span><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">冇暫緩</span></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/PrrEBU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/PrrEBU</a><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">(懶既直接係最底copy) </span></span></div><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20d5a57e7f927dfc4d929fd816a65ce63c3aa1b7","tid":1258810,"uid":1834,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T09:45:31.000Z","msg":"係咪想引人講港獨<br />\